# Product Overview

# **Product Name**

CrossClip

# **Description**

CrossClip is a cross-device clipboard application that allows users to store and synchronize clipboard items including text, images, and files across devices in real time.

**Core Features**

- Email/password authentication
- Password reset
- Clipboard item creation
- Clipboard history (50 items)
- Pin clipboard item
- Delete clipboard item
- Real-time sync
- Item filtering
- Mobile responsive UI
- Dark mode
